      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 2 min or until starting to soften</p>",
